{
  "texts": [
    "We also noted that our proposed method relies on predefined sample dimensions and shapes.",
    "Future extension of our method from these two aspects is needed, i.e., extending from 2D plate to 3D samples and considering different sample shapes.",
    "The ultimate goal of our research is to provide knowledge that helps to build a real-time, cost-efficient diagnosing system for civil structures.",
    "Scientific Reports | (2024) 14:4439 | https://doi.org/10.1038/s41598-024-54494-y",
